# https://github.com/BurntSushi/ripgrep/blob/master/GUIDE.md
#
# Don't forget to export RIPGREP_CONFIG_PATH=~/.ripgreprc

# Case sensitive only if mixed case needle
--smart-case

# Follow symlinks
--follow

# Search hidden files and folders
--hidden

# ... but don't plumb git
--glob=!.git/

# Sort by file path (note: this inhibits parallelism)
--sort=path
